post.description:
Example of POST body:

```
POST /apix/v1/nodes
{
"parent" : "workspace://SpacesStore/d5dac928-e581-4507-9be7-9a2416adc318", 
"name" : "mydocument.txt", 
"type" : "{http://www.alfresco.org/model/content/1.0}content", 
"properties" : {
      "{namespace}property1": [
        "string"
      ],
      "{namespace}property2": [
        "string"
      ],
      "{namespace}property3": [
        "string"
      ]
}, 
"aspectsToAdd" : [
      "{namespace}aspect1"
], 
"aspectsToRemove" : [
      "{namespace}aspect1"
], 
"copyFrom" : "workspace://SpacesStore/f0d15919-3841-4170-807f-b81d2ebdeb80", 
}
```
"aspectsToRemove" is only relevant when copying a node.
